metadata.name: Artichoke, 2009
metadata.description:
A playful composition exploring repetition, color temperature, opacity, and the contrast between texture and flat application of color. 

Original Artwork Information

Media: Acrylic and graphite on canvas
Dimensions: 18 x 18 x 0.75 inches (20.3 x 20.3 x 1.9 cm), with painted wraparound
Availability: Yes; first buyer is entitled to shipment of original work. Please contact the artist on Twitter or via erin@erinrehil.com with shipping address. Shipping costs included in NFT price. Please claim work within 60 days.
